 "description"
 "Non-profit religious-corp civilian PRE-disaster substrate: prevention / mitigation / preparedness / early warning. The 'before' half of the disaster cycle; response (during) is kazaori (ADR-2605263200) and sonae MUST NOT do response (N3, clean phase boundary). Hazard watch from OPEN government feeds (USGS / PHIVOLCS / JMA / GDACS / Copernicus EMS / WMO GTS) → community risk assessment → official-warning RELAY (relay-only, authoritativeSource cited) → preparedness planning + stockpile pre-positioning → drills → imminence signal handoff to kazaori. NOT military (G5+N1; force separate per ADR-2605192315). NO false authority (G8 — MUST NOT originate official seismic/tsunami warnings; relayOnly const true). NO unilateral disaster declaration (G10 — only kazaori Council Lv6+ >=4/7 may declare). NO commercial disaster-prediction software (G4: One Concern / FloodFlash / Jupiter Intelligence / RMS / Tomorrow.io enterprise / Everbridge / OnSolve / AlertMedia PROHIBITED per Charter Rider §2(e)+§2(c)). NO surveillance (G6: open feeds + opt-in self-report only; no individual tracking / no person-profiling). Murakumo-only inference (G7). Community-scale only (G3; NOT national early-warning replacement). Sendai Framework + Sphere reference (G9). 6 cells / 6 Lexicons / 12 gates / 12 non-goals."}
